Website Title: The Card Board

Statement of Purpose:
The pupose of The Card Board is to allow users to post their deck lists on the website and get advice from other players on how to improve. It will give users a platform to search through and compile cards into their own arrays where they can choose to post them publicly or privately.

Version 1 Features: 
	Sign in / Sign up
	Create / View / Update / Delete card arrays
	Create / View / Delete comments associated with deck arrays
	Browse ~17,000 card database with images

Version 2 Features:
	Advanced Browsing (more searching options)
	Card / Deck pricing
	Deck playtesting environment
	Karma system for helping people out

